Sentencas: NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders were synthesized through a hydrothermal process without an additional mixing of NiO and YSZ nanopowders.
Titulo: Porous NiO-YSZ and Ni-YSZ composites fabricated using NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and WO3 additive

Sentencas: Porous Ni-yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) composites, Ni-YSZ composites, with high porosity (25.0-32.8%) were fabricated by reducing NiO-YSZ composites in (94% Ar + 6% H-2) gas.
Titulo: Porous NiO-YSZ and Ni-YSZ composites fabricated using NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and WO3 additive

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity (14,221 cm(-1) at 30 degrees C) and bending strength (130 MPa) of Ni-YSZ composites were enhanced by the addition of WO3 (0.1 wt% WO3) to NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders.
Titulo: Porous NiO-YSZ and Ni-YSZ composites fabricated using NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and WO3 additive

Sentencas: Furthermore, the Y-2(WO4)(3) with a negative coefficient of thermal expansion (CTE) reduced the CTE of Ni-YSZ composites.
Titulo: Porous NiO-YSZ and Ni-YSZ composites fabricated using NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and WO3 additive

Sentencas: The CTE values of 0 and 0.6 wt% WO3-added Ni-YSZ composites were 13.8 x 10(-6) and 12.4 x 10(-6) degrees C-1, respectively.
Titulo: Porous NiO-YSZ and Ni-YSZ composites fabricated using NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and WO3 additive

Sentencas: We demonstrate the fabrication of NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and the addition of WO3 to the NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders are highly effective methods for the fabrication of high-quality Ni-YSZ anode materials in solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Porous NiO-YSZ and Ni-YSZ composites fabricated using NiO-YSZ composite nanopowders and WO3 additive
